roomstore - an irc journaller using cassandra

to run, use

java -jar roomstore.jar:commons-cli.jar:cassandra-driver-core.jar:cassandra-all.jar:snappy-java.jar:slf4j-api.jar:guava.jar:netty.jar:metrics-core.jar:jackson-core-asl.jar:jackson-mapper-asl.jar:libthrift.jar:pircbot.jar -nick your_nick -irc_server irc.freenode.net -channels ubuntu cassandra -endpoints 127.0.0.1

(or you can edit and run -- ant run)

roomstore is Apache2 licensed.

The following commands are available

~ seen username                 -- sends the last message the user sent in this channel (if it exists)
~ today                         -- dumps all messages posted today
~ date MM/yy/dddd               -- dumps all messages from that day

all responses are sent via private message.
